quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,Alif-Lâm-Râ. Ezi ziiVesi zeNcwadi yaye ziyi’Kur’ân ecacileyo
  15,2,Kuya kuba kangakanani na kwabo bangakholwayo ukunqwenela ukuba akwaba babengamaMuslim (ngoMhla woVuko)
  15,3,"Bayeke ke batye, bonwabe, bazilibazise ngamathemba (obuxoki). Kungekudala baza kwazi"
  15,4,ASizanga Sitshabalalise nasiphi na isixeko kungekho mmiselo waso waziwayo
  15,5,Akukho sizwe sinokwenza ixesha laso esilibekelweyo likhawuleze okanye libuyiselwe umva
  15,6,"Kananjalo bathi: “Hini na (Muhammad) iDthikr2 ithunyelwe kubani na? Inene wena ushiywa ziingqondo"
  15,7,Kutheni kaloku ungakhe uze neengelosi kuthi ukuba uthetha inyaniso?”
  15,8,Thina Asizithumeli iingelosi zihle phantsi ngaphandle kokuba zizise inyaniso (isohlwayo) Yaye Sisakwenza njalo) akuyi kubakho kurhoxiswa kwasohlwayo (kubantu abangakholwayo)
  15,9,Inene Sithi kanye abathumele iDthikr (i’Kur’ân kwaye Siza kuyilondoloza ngokwenene (ekoniweni)
  15,10,Inene Thina Sathumela (abaProfeti) ngaphambili kunawe (Muhammad) kubantu ngabantu bamandulo
  15,11,Ke kaloku akukho Mprofeti abakha bangamgculeli akufika kubo
  15,12,Sibenza bungene kanjalo ke (ubuhedeni) ezintliziyweni zabenzi bobubi
  15,13,Abakholwa kuyo (i’Kur’ân) kanti ke umzekelo (woko kwenziwa kwabamandulo sele ufikelele (elwazini lwabo)
  15,14,"Kanti nokuba beSingade Sibavulele isango ezulwini emabangene ngalo, baze bamane ukungena ngalo (imini yonke)"
  15,15,"Ngokungathandabuzekiyo (ukutshona kwelanga) bebeza kuthi: “Amehlo ethu (anokuba) ebephanyakile (besingaboni zingelosi okanye izulu thina) koko besithakathiwe.”"
  15,16,"Inene Thina Sibeke iinkwenkwezi ezinkulu ezulwini, Salihombisa kwabalibukeleyo"
  15,17,Yaye Sililondolozile kuye nawuphi na uShaytân owaqalekiswayo
  15,18,"Ngaphandle kwaloo (Shaytân) uye aye kubisa, aphulaphule aze aleqwe ngedangatya lomlilo ovuthayo"
  15,19,"Kanti wona umhlaba Siwandlalile, Sabeka apho kuwo iintaba, Senza ukuba kuhlume zonke iitlobo-ntlobo zezinto zaba ngomlinganiselo oqingqiweyo"
  15,20,"Kananjalo apho Sinike iimbonelelo ngendlela yokuphila kwenu nezo zinto zingabonelelwa nini (izilwanyana eziphilayo, iinkomo izinambuzane njl-njl)"
  15,21,"Yaye akukho nanye into engenawo umsindleko wayo kuThi, kananjalo aSiwuthumeli kuyo ngaphandle komlinganiselo owaziwayo"
  15,22,"Ke kaloku Thina Sithumela imimoya echumisayo, Size Senze amanzi (emvula) ehle esibhakabhakeni, Siwanike nina nisele, ayinini ke abanini vimba bawo"
  15,23,"Kananjalo inene SiThi kanye abanika ubomi, Senze nokufa, yaye Thina Siziindlalifa"
  15,24,"Inene Thina Siyazazi izizukulwana zokuqala zenu ezadlulayo, Siyasazi kananjalo esi sizukulwana senu sikhoyo, ukanti Siyazazi nezisezayo, emva kwenu"
  15,25,"Inene iNkosi yakho Iza kubaqokelela ndaweninye bonke. Inene Yona nguSobulumko, uSolwazi"
  15,26,Kananjalo Samdala umntu ngodongwe olomileyo olwajikwa lwaba ludaka
  15,27,"Zona iiJinni, Sazidala ngaphambili (kunomntu) ngomlilo ongenamsi"
  15,28,"Yabona! INkosi yakho Yathi kwiingelosi: “Ndiza kudala umntu ngodongwe olomileyo olwenziwe udaka"
  15,29,"Ndakuba Ndimgqibile ngokupheleleyo, Ndamphefumlela ngomoya eNdiwudalele yena, nina niya kuguqa phantsi niqubude kuye.”"
  15,30,Ke kaloku iingelosi zaqubuda zonke kuye
  15,31,Kwasala uIblîs (uSathana)! Yena wala ukuba ngomnye wabo baqubudayo
  15,32,"(UAllâh) Wathi: “Hini na Iblîs! Kungani na wena ukuba ungabi ngomnye wabo baqubudayo?”"
  15,33,"(UIblîs) wathi: “Mna andinguye onokuqubuda emntwini, Omdale ngodongwe olomileyo olwenziwe udaka.”"
  15,34,"Wathi (uAllâh): “Phuma umke apha kuba inene wena , ungoqalekisiweyo"
  15,35,Kwaye inene wena isiqalekiso siya kuba phezu kwakho kude kube yiMini yoVuko (lwabafileyo).”
  15,36,"(UIblîs) wathi: “O Nkosi yam! Ndirhoxisele isohlwayo kude kube yiMini yoVuko (lwabafileyo).”"
  15,37,"Wathi uAllâh: “Ngoko ke ungomnye wabo barhoxiselweyo isohlwayo sabo"
  15,38,"Kude kube yiMini etyunjiweyo,”"
  15,39,"Wathi: (uIblîs: “O Nkosi yam! Ngenxa yokuba Undibeke ekulahlekeni, inene mna ndiya kuyihombisa indlela eya ekulahlekeni kubo (abantu) emhlabeni, yaye ndiya kubalahlekisa bonke"
  15,40,Ngaphandle kwezicaka zakho ezinyanisekileyo kubo.”
  15,41,"(UAllâh) wathi: “Le yiNdlela engqale kuM Ngqo"
  15,42,"Inene wena awuyi kuba nagunya phezu kwezicaka zaM, ngaphandle kwabo balandela wena bazii-Ghrâwûn"
  15,43,Yaye isiHogo likhaya labo lesithembiso bonke
  15,44,"Sona (isiHogo) sinamasango asixhenxe, ngalinye kuloo masango kukho udidi (olulodwa lwaboni) olugcinwe apho"
  15,45,Inene bona abaMoyikayo uAllâh baya kuba phakathi eMiyezweni enemithombo yamanzi (ePaladesi)
  15,46,"(Kuya kuthiwa kubo): “Ngenani phakathi ngoxolo, nikhuselekile"
  15,47,"Yaye Thina Siya kususa nasiphi na isixhiba abanaso ezintliziyweni zabo omnye komnye. Baya kuba ngabazalwana, bajongane, ubuso ngobuso, besezihlalweni eziphakamileyo"
  15,48,"Akukho kudinwa kuya kubafumana bona apho, bengayi kugxothwa nakugxothwa apho"
  15,49,"Vakalisa ke wena (Muhammad) ezicakeni zaM okokuba inene Mna NdinguMxoleli, uSozinceba"